---
/**
 * DKART LINE — Future & Partnership Section
 * Explains upcoming developments and calls for support/sponsorship.
 */
---

<section id="future" class="future dk-grain">
  <div class="future__container">
    <div class="future__header dk-reveal">
      <span class="future__label">Notre Vision</span>
      <h2 class="future__title dk-display">
        Ce n'est que<br /><span class="dk-text-accent">le début</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="future__subtitle">
        Le kart est fonctionnel, mais notre vision va beaucoup plus loin. On
        veut faire encore mieux, encore plus ergonomique, toujours plus
        innovant.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="future__grid">
      <!-- R&D Card -->
      <div class="future__card dk-reveal" style="transition-delay: 0.1s">
        <div class="future__card-icon">🚀</div>
        <h3 class="future__card-title dk-display">Recherche & Développement</h3>
        <p class="future__card-text">
          Nous noircissons nos pages d'idées pour repousser les limites de nos
          drift karts. Le projet est loin d'être terminé, soyez attentifs à la
          suite !
        </p>
        <div class="future__image-wrapper">
          <img src="/images/Kart-la_suite.jpeg" alt="Kart en développement pour la suite" class="future__image" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Partenariat Card -->
      <div
        class="future__card future__card--accent dk-reveal"
        style="transition-delay: 0.2s"
      >
        <div class="future__card-icon">🤝</div>
        <h3 class="future__card-title dk-display">Soutenir le projet</h3>
        <p class="future__card-text">
          Nous sommes quatre étudiants passionnés. Pour continuer cette aventure
          dans les meilleures conditions, nous recherchons des <strong
            >coups de main</strong
          >, que ce soit sous forme de dons de matériel (pièces, outillage) ou
          de soutien financier.
        </p>

        <div class="future__alert">
          <h4 class="future__alert-title">Défiscalisation jusqu'à 66%</h4>
          <p class="future__alert-text">
            Soutenez-nous via la <strong>Fondation de l'UTT</strong> ! Vos dons (financiers
            ou matériels) peuvent bénéficier d'une <strong>défiscalisation de 66%</strong>
            pour les particuliers (60% pour les entreprises).
          </p>

          <div class="future__donations mt-4">
            <div class="future__donation-item">
              <span class="future__donation-value">50€</span>
              <span class="future__donation-cost">(= 17€*)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="future__donation-item">
              <span class="future__donation-value">100€</span>
              <span class="future__donation-cost">(= 34€*)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="future__donation-item">
              <span class="future__donation-value">200€</span>
              <span class="future__donation-cost">(= 68€*)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="future__donation-item">
              <span class="future__donation-value">500€</span>
              <span class="future__donation-cost">(= 170€*)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="future__donation-item">
              <span class="future__donation-value">1000€</span>
              <span class="future__donation-cost">(= 340€*)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="future__donation-item">
              <span class="future__donation-value">2000€</span>
              <span class="future__donation-cost">(= 680€*)</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="future__alert-note">*Coût réel après déduction fiscale pour un particulier</p>

          <a href="/contact" class="dk-btn dk-btn--outline dk-btn--sm mt-4" style="width: 100%; justify-content: center; text-align: center;">
            Faire un don
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .future {
    padding: calc(var(--dk-space-3xl) + 40px) var(--dk-space-lg)
      var(--dk-space-3xl);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #080c12 0%, #0a1628 50%, #0d1f3c 100%);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .future__container {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .future__header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--dk-space-3xl);
  }

  .future__label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--dk-font-display);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    color: var(--dk-accent);
    margin-bottom: var(--dk-space-sm);
    padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(var(--dk-accent-rgb), 0.3);
  }

  .future__title {
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 5rem);
    margin-bottom: var(--dk-space-md);
    color: var(--dk-text);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .future__subtitle {
    font-family: var(--dk-font-body);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--dk-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .future__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--dk-space-xl);
  }

  .future__card {
    background: var(--dk-bg-elevated);
    border: 1px solid var(--dk-border);
    padding: var(--dk-space-xl);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    height: 100%;
    transition:
      transform var(--dk-transition-slow),
      box-shadow var(--dk-transition-slow),
      border-color var(--dk-transition);
  }

  .future__card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-10px);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
    border-color: rgba(var(--dk-accent-rgb), 0.3);
  }

  .future__card--accent {
    border-color: rgba(var(--dk-accent-rgb), 0.4);
    background: linear-gradient(
      to bottom right,
      var(--dk-bg-elevated),
      rgba(var(--dk-accent-rgb), 0.08)
    );
  }

  .future__card--accent:hover {
    border-color: var(--dk-accent);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(var(--dk-accent-rgb), 0.2);
  }

  .future__card-icon {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--dk-space-md);
    line-height: 1;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 15px rgba(var(--dk-accent-rgb), 0.3));
    transition: transform var(--dk-transition);
  }

  .future__card:hover .future__card-icon {
    transform: scale(1.1) rotate(5deg);
  }

  .future__card-title {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: var(--dk-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--dk-space-sm);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .future__card-text {
    font-family: var(--dk-font-body);
    color: var(--dk-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--dk-space-sm);
  }

  .future__card-text strong {
    color: var(--dk-text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .future__image-wrapper {
    margin-top: var(--dk-space-xs);
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
  }

  .future__image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
    transition: transform var(--dk-transition-slow);
  }

  .future__card:hover .future__image {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  .future__alert {
    background: rgba(var(--dk-accent-rgb), 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(var(--dk-accent-rgb), 0.2);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--dk-accent);
    padding: var(--dk-space-md) var(--dk-space-lg);
    margin-top: auto;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .future__alert::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    right: 0;
    width: 100px;
    height: 100px;
    background: radial-gradient(
      circle,
      rgba(var(--dk-accent-rgb), 0.1) 0%,
      transparent 70%
    );
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .future__alert-title {
    font-family: var(--dk-font-display);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--dk-accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .future__alert-text {
    font-family: var(--dk-font-body);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--dk-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .future__alert-text strong {
    color: var(--dk-text);
  }

  .future__donations {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--dk-space-sm);
  }

  .future__donation-item {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 0.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.35rem;
  }

  .future__donation-item:hover {
    border-color: rgba(var(--dk-accent-rgb), 0.5);
    background: rgba(var(--dk-accent-rgb), 0.1);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .future__donation-value {
    font-family: var(--dk-font-display);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--dk-text);
  }

  .future__donation-cost {
    font-family: var(--dk-font-body);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--dk-accent);
  }

  .future__alert-note {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--dk-secondary);
    font-style: italic;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .mt-4 {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .future {
      padding: calc(var(--dk-space-3xl) + 60px) var(--dk-space-md)
        var(--dk-space-2xl);
    }

    .future__header {
      margin-bottom: var(--dk-space-xl);
    }

    .future__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--dk-space-lg);
    }

    .future__card {
      padding: var(--dk-space-lg) var(--dk-space-md);
    }

    .future__card-icon {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: var(--dk-space-sm);
    }

    .future__card-title {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .future__alert {
      padding: var(--dk-space-md);
      margin-top: var(--dk-space-lg);
      border-left-width: 3px;
    }

    .future__alert-title {
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }

    .future__title {
      font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 10vw, 3.5rem);
    }
  }
</style>
